{
  "stem": "1736.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] So-- but it's something that's stayed with me my whole life, is that when my turn came, and the teacher was to look after me, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] he actually got hold of me, and dunked me under the water, and forcibly tried to keep me under.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was no way of trying to teach me how to swim.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He really wanted to cause me harm.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, I don't know how far he would have gone or what he would have did.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But all I know is that I managed to get out of his grip, and managed to come up, spewing water and all this sort of thing, and then running home.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But to me, that was the first incident, really something that said to me, hey, you're being treated-- you're being singled out for bad treatment.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[SIGHS] [INTERPOSING VOICES]",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was a sports teacher who I had no other dealings with.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But everybody knew that I was a Jew.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, I wasn't part of the youth movement-- you know, the Hitler Youth.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I wasn't this.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I wasn't allowed to go here.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And by that-- in a small town, these things get-- it gets around very quickly.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "On top of it, I think that was also a certain knowledge that my father [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] had done reasonably well.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was a guy in the town that had a motor car, and I was the son, all that.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, and you have all these things that go with it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But that was my first incident of really noticing this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And, of course, from then on, I had to look out, And I was very much aware of the situation.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, and you might ask me, did I complain about it?",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
